\
General:\
\
1. The background is far too dark. In the design example the background is more like #f8f8f8.\
2. There is no separate of background between the main container and the header. This makes it look slick.\
3. There should be a small school chooser in the header that lets user toggle between schools if they are part of more than one school in the database.\
4. There should be more space between elements in the menu. \
6. The menu should be collapsable. This is especially important for mobile. On mobile it should probably move to a hamburger icon or something similar.\
