Home\
1. This needs a complete rework to present the data in a better way. The idea of having priorities is correct but they need to look better and have more consistency (e.g. the cohort change doesn\'92t automatically show.)\
2. The student support priorities look cramped and strange. The pills shouldn\'92t be underneath the aims.\
3. The positive momentum and leave appropavals cards are dated and don\'92t make sense. Please take inspiration from the cards on the design example.\
4. There are 4 hero cards in the design example - this could be utilised in our app. This should be the key events in the data.\
5. Teacher names should always be accompanied with a profile picture. This makes it look far more professional.\
